{"tid":2204682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"收藏家符春曉油麻地寓所遇竊　報稱值40億毛澤東字畫及郵票被盜","createTime":"2020-09-16T08:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T09:27:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f68e0f2e39e369e3767250df2e456a04117e79dc","tid":2204682,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:49:13.000Z","msg":"上周四（9月10日）下午，警方接獲報案稱，油麻地彌敦道510號一大廈單位遇竊。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，單位內價值逾40億元的古董郵票及字畫失竊，遇竊單位業主為著名郵票收藏家符春曉，是次被偷走的為毛澤東郵票、以及毛澤東的親筆字畫、手稿等。<br />\n<br />\n符春曉為香港郵學會會員，他曾接受傳媒訪問稱，最愛收集早期毛澤東的郵品，因為較罕見。"},{"pid":"51a9c13dcf6e0e487d03eac87f6e86c3820833d2","tid":2204682,"uid":82397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"保險？"},{"pid":"ecdbd69267efb463ff3396dba08c0d7b994ef58f","tid":2204682,"uid":93649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:50:02.000Z","msg":"你話80億都得啦"},{"pid":"3f833b194d44c6a93b57d8f4c00b615c68d233b7","tid":2204682,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecdbd69267efb463ff3396dba08c0d7b994ef58f","tid":2204682,"uid":93649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:50:02.000Z","msg":"你話80億都得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:51:36.000Z","msg":"張屌明都過千萬 老毛40億真係唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3091df416c77296e156ca35d8323f26a44359dc8","tid":2204682,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f833b194d44c6a93b57d8f4c00b615c68d233b7","tid":2204682,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecdbd69267efb463ff3396dba08c0d7b994ef58f","tid":2204682,"uid":93649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:50:02.000Z","msg":"你話80億都得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:51:36.000Z","msg":"張屌明都過千萬 老毛40億真係唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:04:24.000Z","msg":"攞嚟抿屎都嫌污糟"},{"pid":"272fc410906c0a09bb845254173c4e